oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: John Jared fishing at Rutledge Falls on Crumpton Creek
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of John Jared fishing at Rutledge Falls on Crumpton Creek. Jared is standing on an embankment with trees, brush, Rutledge Falls and rocks in the background. Jared is wearing cap, fishing vest, pants and his holding fishing rod.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
